title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 §§ 210-5.1 - Warranty requirement
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 §§ 210-5.1 - Warranty requirement

State Regulations

Manufacturers shall provide the warranty and warranty
statement required by California Code of Regulations, title 13, sections
2445.1
and
2445.2
(see Table 1, section
200.9
of this Title) for personal
watercraft produced and delivered for sale in New York. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6
§§
210-5.1

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
